# macOS Finder duplicate files (autonomously created on iCloud-synced trees;
# named "foo 2.ts", "foo 3.svelte", etc.). They break Vite imports + svelte-check
# when they sneak into the docker build context.
**/* [0-9].*
**/* [0-9][0-9].*
**/._*
